T1  - Making a NARCO: Childhood Exposure to Illegal Labor Markets and Criminal Life Paths
AU  - Sviatschi, Maria Micaela
Y1  - 2022/07/01
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2022/07/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA17082
